# Tending to cause [[giggle]]s.
#:''The crabbed and hunched old man selling his assortment of neon pink little-girls' accessories and gangsta' rap CDs was ever a '''gigglesome''' sight.''
# Tending to have [[the giggles]].
#:''An extremely cute clerk worked at the counter, and an endless stream of '''gigglesome''' teenage girls would pester him for help.

====Synonyms====
*(''tending to cause giggles''): [[funny]], [[humorous]]
